# Component-level `styles/` folder (`src/components/`)

SFC pulls **external** styles via `<style lang="scss" src="...">` (or CSS) — typically **250-line** `.vue` cap ([code-size-decomposition.mdc](code-size-decomposition.mdc)).

## Placement

- Files under **`src/components/<bucket>/<FeatureName>/styles/`** (**`styles`** inside same folder as feature `.vue`).
- **No** standalone **`*.scss`** / **`*.css`** beside **`.vue`** at feature root (not `DialogFoo/DialogFoo.unscoped.scss` beside `DialogFoo.vue`).
- **`src/layouts/`**, **`src/pages/`**: same pattern if external sheet needed — **`styles/`** next to **`.vue`**, not loose siblings.

## Naming

- **Feature-scoped** basename, e.g. **`WindowAppStyling.unscoped.scss`**, **`WindowAppStyling.floatingWindowPopTransition.unscoped.scss`**, **`DialogKeybindSettings.unscoped.scss`** — multiple sheets under **`styles/`** stay distinguishable.
- **`_variables.scss`** (fixed name): feature/layout/page **`$` theme variables** re-exported through [quasar.variables.scss](src/css/quasar.variables.scss). **Not** second `<style src>` — **`@use`d** from other SCSS only. Start with **`@use` … [app.palette.scss](src/css/app.palette.scss) `as *`** when needed; **no** barrel **`@use`** from here. New feature tokens here, not monolith. **Keep every name SFC/foundation catalogue still references** — removal → **Sass undefined variable** at build, not Stylelint. [project-scss.mdc](project-scss.mdc) **Theme token layout**; **`$q*`** only → **`yarn audit:quasar-component-tokens`**.
- Scoped blocks may stay in SFC; **unscoped** or large extracts often **`.unscoped.scss`** suffix when matches dialogs/windows.

## Wiring

- SFC relative import into `styles/`:

```vue
<style lang="scss" src="./styles/WindowAppStyling.unscoped.scss"></style>
```

- SFC block order: **`<template>`**, **`<script>`**, **`<style>`** last ([vue-quasar.mdc](vue-quasar.mdc)).

